## Pile of playing cards

a pile is a list of cards
a pile has a name as text
a pile has an appearance as one of stacked, staggered or fanned

-- cards can only be in one pile at a time
to add a card to a pile
	if the current-pile of the card is defined
		remove the card from its current-pile
	append the card to the pile
	set the current-pile of the card to the pile

